### [User] 결제 요청 (PG 콜백 대기, 최대 10초)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/payments
X-Loopers-LoginId: usertest123
X-Loopers-LoginPw: abc123!@#
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9814-1451"
}

###

### [PG Simulator] 결제 콜백 (인증 불필요)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/payments/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionKey": "TX-001",
  "orderId": "1",
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9814-1451",
  "amount": 100000,
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "reason": null
}

###

### [User] 결제 상태 조회 (PENDING이면 PG Poll 후 반환)
GET {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/payments/1
X-Loopers-LoginId: usertest123
X-Loopers-LoginPw: abc123!@#

###
